rows.label: qst102501_msg001
rows.name:
My respected teacher went to
gather Dragon Incense (temp)

rows.label: qst102501_msg002
rows.name:
I'm worried, so please bring
my teacher back (temp)

rows.label: qst102501_msg101
rows.name: Bring him back quickly (temp)

rows.label: qst102501_msg0001
rows.name: Teacher is very late, mo...

rows.label: qst102501_msg0002
rows.name:
Have you seen Teacher
Guztin anywhere, mo?

rows.label: qst102501_msg0003
rows.name: I see, mo...

rows.label: qst102501_msg0004
rows.name:
He left saying he was going
to request a job from the
Hræsvelgr Mercenary Corps...

rows.label: qst102501_msg0005
rows.name:
But no matter how long I wait,
he doesn't come back, mo...

rows.label: qst102501_msg0006
rows.name:
I asked the Hræsvelgr mercenaries
who came to Fonsa Myma, but they said
they didn't know anything, mo...

rows.label: qst102501_msg0007
rows.name:
Teacher Guztin... What
should Pilolo do, mo...?

rows.label: qst102501_msg0008
rows.name: Momo? You'll look for him, mo?

rows.label: qst102501_msg0009
rows.name:
Are you from the Hræsvelgr
Mercenary Corps, mo?

rows.label: qst102501_msg0010
rows.name:
What a fortunate meeting!
Pilolo is so moved, mo!

rows.label: qst102501_msg0011
rows.name:
Then, let me formally
request this of you, mo.

rows.label: qst102501_msg0012
rows.name: I want you to find Teacher Guztin, mo.

rows.label: qst102501_msg0013
rows.name:
Teacher headed for the Hræsvelgr
village, but it seems he
hasn't arrived yet, mo.

rows.label: qst102501_msg0014
rows.name: I'm counting on you, mo...

rows.label: qst102501_msg0015
rows.name: I just hope teacher is safe...

rows.label: qst102501_msg0101
rows.name:
Teacher Guztin is researching
Divine Beasts, mo.

rows.label: qst102501_msg0102
rows.name:
This time, he was supposed to go
inside Invidia to get something
essential for his research, mo...

rows.label: qst102501_msg0103
rows.name: Teacher... Please be safe, mo...
